Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么还不睡 已经中午了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why are you still awake? It's the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在重新制定我的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm redrawing my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被卡米拉洗脑了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla's gotten inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若要让她的计谋成功 我们必须迅速行动\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If her scheme is going to work, we need to move fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抢在人类重新控制有关地区之前\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}before the humans regain control over the region in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得人类不太可能做到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't think that's likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦拉吉亚的首都一直没有情报传来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's been no intelligence from the capital of Wallachia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能正在准备行动\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They could be preparing for a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能都死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or they're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能确定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须把这点考虑进去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So I have to factor that in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该睡觉了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You should sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以在耗光所有士兵之前\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can possibly push east as far as Lake Balaton
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向东推进到巴拉顿湖\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}before I run out of soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那样会暴露我们的西部边境\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but that exposes our Western border.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有丽诺尔说服锻造师 我们才能做到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can't do it without Lenore turning the forgemaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她只是带他出去散他妈的步\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and she's just taking him out for fucking walkies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会搞定他的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She will land him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们行动必须要快\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's going to have to be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上床吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Come to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有武器 补给线\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And the weapons! The supply lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都计划好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I worked all that out earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -只是金钱和时间的问题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- What? - It's just money and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我算过了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I did the calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你算算这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then calculate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要尸体 但也需要为我们供血的活口\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need dead bodies, but we also need feeding stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫克托能把从这里到巴拉顿湖的所有人类都变成黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector can make every human from here to Balaton into a night creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那样会让我们失去所有食物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but that leaves us with nothing to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你肯定知道 施第里尔周边地区是如何保卫边界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but surely you know how the regions surrounding Styria defend their borders
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对抗城堡中四个可怕的吸血鬼女王的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}against the four terrible vampire women in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用士兵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}With soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没那么多士兵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They don't have that many soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那都是雇佣兵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They hire mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 士兵 雇佣兵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. Soldiers, mercenaries,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地方武力...有什么区别呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}local forces... what's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,区别是雇佣兵可以被敌对方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The difference is that mercenaries can be rehired
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以更高的价钱雇过来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}by the opposing side for more money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是... 那样并不光荣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But... there's no honor in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实不光荣 但是有钱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, but there is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们可以耗尽准备对付我们的力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So we can deplete the forces rallied against us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照你的意愿部署我们雇来的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and deploy the men we buy, as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真能办到吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You can actually do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个行政问题 而且我已经解决了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was an administrative problem, and I solved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就不能小声点吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can you not keep it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我隔着几堵墙和三个打鼾的男孩 都能听见你们说话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can hear you through several walls and three snoring boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I do not want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们大中午的在做什么啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are you doing in the middle of the bloody day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完善你的计谋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Making your scheme work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不需要"完善" 本来就很高明\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You don't have to "make" it work. It was bloody genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 我要去睡了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good morning. I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然现在大家都醒了 不如一起喝一杯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, we're all awake now, we might as well have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以告诉我 你是怎么完善我的计谋的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you can tell me how you helped with my scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说那是"计谋"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You call it a scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是计谋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is a scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无礼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你坚持的话...我们可以喝一杯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But if you insist... we can have a drink
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后告诉你 我们将如何在明年统治一个帝国\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and tell you how we'll be ruling an empire next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前提是丽诺尔能完成她的任务\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If Lenore can do her part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我必须喝一杯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, now I definitely need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就像他妈的收养了他一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think she's fucking adopted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有事瞒着我们 你知道吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's holding things back from us, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很孤独 想让我们留下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's lonely. He wants us to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他确实杀了他的父亲\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, he did kill his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及帮他离开的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And the people who helped him left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就他自己在一座死城堡中守卫一间破房子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's just him in a dead castle guarding a ruined house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这似乎不公平 对吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It doesn't seem fair, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他除掉了德古拉的世界 只得到这样的回报\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He rid the world of Dracula, and this is his reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他认为自己活该\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think that he thinks he deserves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤独吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了自己的亲生父亲\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He killed his own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想为此受罚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He wants to be punished for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他没有其他选择\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Even though he had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看样子 他可能也杀了阿町\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It seems that he probably killed Cho, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少阿町是因为他袭击德古拉而死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}At the very least, Cho died as a result of his attack on Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在家乡比以往任何时候都更不受保护了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Now home is more unprotected than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他有太多神奇的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he has so many wonderful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能为我们做很多 给我们一个未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He can do so much for us. Give us a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他留在这\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he stays here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在不自杀的情况下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because it's as close to death as he can manage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最接近死亡的方式了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}without killing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该为他做点什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We should do something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他一个奖励\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Give him a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先让我睡一觉好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can it be after I've had a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了很多书 头痛死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've read so much, my brain hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真懒\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是懒\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是为重要工作保留体力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I conserve my resources for important efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如吃饭\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我们是不是没吃午饭\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God, did we miss lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许阿鲁卡多可以再做一顿午饭\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe Alucard can make lunch again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还有晚饭  -再做一顿晚饭吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- And dinner. - One more dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实早晚有一天 我又得开始自己做饭了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, sooner or later, I'll have to start preparing my own food again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别人做的饭味道更好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And meals taste better when someone else makes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我经常这么说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's what I always say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午饭和晚饭\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lunch and dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看晚上的情况再说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and we'll see what the night brings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又在到处乱走吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you wandering around again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 完全不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}N-n-no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在出去之前活动活动腿脚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just stretching my legs before I go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这膝盖已经不如从前了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The knees, you know. Not what they used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我花了太多时间蹲着看你那些精彩绝伦的书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I spent too much time crouching down with your wonderful books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说真的 很精彩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}H-Honestly. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我学习到很多东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've learned so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你... 学习到了什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What... have you learned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这个地方以前的居住者中有很多人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, I believe many of the previous occupants of this place
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对接触地狱本身有着真正的兴趣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}had a real interest in contacting Hell itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我们不是...我是说...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You mean we are not the... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前就发生过吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}this has happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去就有吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚地了解到曾有人试图\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's clear to me that there have been attempts
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这打开一扇地狱之门\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to open a door to Hell here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 整个修道院都可能被污染了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In fact, this entire structure could be contaminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我担心你们的健康 萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I worry for your health, Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本人已经出现了讨厌的咳嗽和轻微的跛行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I myself may have developed a nasty cough and a slight limp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不该留在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有两位修道士失踪了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Two of our number have gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的工作就快完成了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But our work is almost done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不够快 萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not soon enough, Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能被遍布在这座建筑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They may have expired from the Satanic poison
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石木中的撒旦的毒药毒死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}permeating the very stones and timbers of this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在不能走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can't leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你必须走 快逃吧 萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But you must! You must flee, Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Flee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得对 院长 就是逃\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're absolutely right, Prior! Flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你告诉我 修道院里有多少人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}why don't you tell me how many of you there are in that priory?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来晚了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像从前那么多了 但也足够了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not as many as there used to be, but more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你们在里面互相残食吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What, have you been eating each other in there or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直有人离开... 已经好几天了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've been leaving... for days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我们几个人 一天出去一个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just a few of us, one a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走到其他城镇 传播消息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Walking to other towns, spreading the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-像感染一样  -像福音传教士一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Like an infection. - Like evangelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传播知识和计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Passing on the knowledge and the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把地狱带到这个被遗弃的世界上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bring Hell to this abandoned Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是萨拉的计划吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is Sala's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们访客的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is our Visitor's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对我们说话了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He spoke to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在脑子里听见了他的声音\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We heard his voice in our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那一刻起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Since that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都无比清晰了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}everything has been clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗生物果然让他们疯掉了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It really did drive them insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许修道士们才是这里的受害人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The monks may actually be the victims here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗生物有魔力 可能扭曲了他们的思想\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Night creatures have magical powers. It may have distorted their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修道院地下有一个黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They've got a night creature under the priory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没杀它 而是把它藏起来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They didn't kill it, they hid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等一下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wait. One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修道院已成一片废墟\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The priory is in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怀疑那里已经不圣洁了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I suspect it's been deconsecrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地下室关着一个黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There is a night creature being held on a basement level,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它周围画着符号\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}symbols drawn around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回廊也在那个地下室\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The Corridor is in that same basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在那里活着的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's alive down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我都没感觉到它有痛苦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes! I didn't even get the sense that it was in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且它离回廊的距离近得可疑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And it's proximity to the Corridor is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得它在等待\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think it's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉和他的人在制定某种计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sala and his men are enacting some kind of plan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中涉及这些炼金术符号\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}involving these alchemical symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们见过的那些符号吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The same symbols we've seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 符号组合\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Indeed! Combined!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修道院老图书馆的书卷缺了几页\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There are pages missing from volumes in the priory's old library.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术的用途果真令人着迷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The application of alchemy is honestly f-fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们完全忽略了修道院藏书中最精彩的部分\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They completely ignored the best part of the books stored in the priory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个经历过死亡和重生的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Two persons who have gone through death and rebirth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可被融成同体者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}can be fused into The Rebis,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术的终极目标\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the ultimate alchemical goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们连想都没想过...  -圣日耳曼 别跑题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- and they didn't even think of it... - Saint Germain. Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好...好的 当然\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Y-Yes, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是错过了完成炼金术的机会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's just, the missed opportunity to complete alchemy itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那能拯救全世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It could save the very world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拯救这个小镇吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let's settle for saving this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我觉得我像是被引领来这里的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Indeed. I feel as if I've been led here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就为找到无限回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}To find the Infinite Corridor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实现哲学的终极目标\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to achieve the ultimate goal of philosophy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且成为... 英雄\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and to be... a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从一个谨慎而恭敬的...距离\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}From a discreet and respectful... distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们完蛋了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We absolutely are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛珐 请你给我翻译一下这个白痴的胡言乱语\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sypha, translate this idiot's gibberish into actual language for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没掌握足够的信息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't have enough information yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要知道 修道院不再圣洁了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All you need to know is that the priory is desecrated
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们在以某种方式和一个活的黑暗生物合作\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they are somehow working with a living night creature
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它教会了他们魔法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}who has taught them magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是 这完全有可能\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sadly, that is all entirely possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能应付那个黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can handle the night creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想先干翻一小群疯狂的僧修道士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but I'd rather not wade through a small army of mad monks to get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会分阶段召集我的武装\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll summon my men-at-arms by stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想引起恐慌或被萨拉发现\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't want to cause alarm or give Sala warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在日落时进攻 到时候镇民们都在家里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We'll strike at sundown, when the townsfolk will be indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛珐和圣日耳曼得跟我去修道院地下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sypha and Saint Germain will need to get under the priory with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的人绝对不能靠近那里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your people shouldn't be anywhere near that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们挖个洞 拦住所有修道士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Make a hole for us, and keep the monks off our backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的有时间等到日落吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do we really have time to wait for sundown?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的镇子 你们听我指挥\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is my town. You do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须讲战术 以人多取胜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We must have strategy and force of numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妥善完成才行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This will be done properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll begin the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说 我为什么要跟你们一起下去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And, why would I be going down there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像没听见你宏伟大计的那部分\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I seem to have missed that part of your epic plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为据你所说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because from what you've said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和无限回廊之间有一只黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}there's a night creature between you and the Infinite Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能只有一次机会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we may only have one chance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你通过 这样你就可以打开回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to get you past it so you can open the Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像没太听懂...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm afraid I don't understa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是...你是在在...帮我吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're... You're actually... helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是...好人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're being... kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了 没必要大惊小怪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right, all right, no need to make a production out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧...很抱歉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well... I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不习惯别人无缘无故对我好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm-I'm-I'm simply not used to people being kind to me for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了 小声点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's enough. Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让任何人听见\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We don't want anyone to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次他看到一个男人想踢一只猫\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He saw a man try to kick a cat once,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果他把那个男人的腿打折了三个地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and he broke the man's leg in three places!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能随便踢猫 不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, you don't do that to cats, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三处骨折 我听见三声\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Three places. I heard three cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的猫咪 它又没害谁\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Poor bloody cat wasn't hurting anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪只想好好活着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Cats just want to get on with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为我们展示了真相\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have shown us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们听了你的话 做好了准备\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have listened. We have prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你所愿 我们禁锢了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have restrained you, as you wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也照你的意思给了你沉思的时间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have given you time to meditate, as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝遗弃了这个世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God has abandoned the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德古拉必须被复活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dracula must be brought back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的目的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是你的锻造师的目的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is what he who forged you would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以访客及其锻造师...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We do this in the name of our Visitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克之名这样做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and his forgemaster, Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日落之时\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}When the sun goes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就做该做之事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}we shall do what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的军械库很漂亮\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The armory here is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我以为会有更神奇的武器\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I expected there to be more magical weapons, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲是一位技艺高超的魔法师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My father was an accomplished magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他本身力量强大\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He held enough power within himself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以觉得魔法增强武器是不必要的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that he felt magically enhanced weapons to be unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢让物质保持原样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He preferred physical things to be themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有强烈的观点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't have a strong opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为魔法和科学是同一枚硬币的两面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Magic and science are two sides of the same coin to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定城堡能移动吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you sure the castle can't be moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没隐瞒我们什么吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's not something you're not telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你对我们有所隐瞒 会告诉我们吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you tell us if there's something you're not telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城堡的某些部分 你故意不让我们看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}there are parts of the castle that you avoid showing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事你从来不谈\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Things you don't talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城堡很大\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's a big castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是像密室这样的老建筑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Filled with centuries of material, like the Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一起的时间多着呢 不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have plenty of time together, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁饿了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Who's hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜幕已经降临了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Has night fallen already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你没听见我进来  -没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- You didn't hear me enter. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有一股气味\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have a scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像... 茉莉花和葡萄酒\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like... jasmine and wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的书吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good book?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我没注意到这枚戒指\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I didn't notice that ring before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我们都戴着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Really? We all wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们四个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡米拉 莫拉娜 斯崔格和我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla, Morana, Striga and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜这其中一定有什么令人不安的原因\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm presuming there's some disturbing reason for that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我会后悔问起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I will regret asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 黑色和红色\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look. The black and the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表黑夜和鲜血\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The night and the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是它们让我们聚在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These are the things that bind us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒指是忠于彼此的标志\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The rings are a sign of loyalty to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是...好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's actually... well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"美好"这个词似乎不合适\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}"nice" seems like the wrong word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是美好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来这是你们的另一面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's a different facet of you all, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像这本书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一本魔法著作 但也是...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's a magical work, but it's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么形容呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}how to describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼哲学 真是令人着迷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Vampire philosophy. It's fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那现在我们不全是恶魔了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So now we're not all monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 承认吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go on, admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我承认这比我想象的更有...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I admit there seems to be more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深度...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}depth to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该叫什么呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}what would you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼文化吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Vampire culture? Than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有关于世界实体存在的观点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There are ideas in here about physical presence in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土壤 景观和生命的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the importance of soil and landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...重要性\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and... being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是哲学 不可思议\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I mean, actual philosophy. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我有一个哲学问题想问你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then I have a philosophical question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当另一个人在笼子里时 很难进行外交\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's hard to do diplomacy when the other person is in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法反驳\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外交就是妥协\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Diplomacy is compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我获得一些好处 你获得一些好处\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I get something, you get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你我都没得到想要的全部的一切 但都能快乐地离开\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Neither of us get everything we want, but we both leave happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我洗耳恭听  -但是你...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- You have my attention. - But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你连离开的机会都没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you don't even get to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没得到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You haven't got anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有权力都在我手上 你只是笼子里的英俊男子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have all the power, and you're a pretty man in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我... 英俊吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm... I'm pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不公平\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It just doesn't seem fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一天没睡 一直在想这件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been awake all day thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 待在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You. Down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要问的是什么 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's the question, Lenore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想被放出去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to be let out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能想到这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's all I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我唯一能为你做的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's the only thing I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你不会直接放我走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But you're not just gonna let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...是不会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忠于我的姐妹们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm loyal to my sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会打开门说 "飞吧 给你自由 英俊的人类男孩"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}To just fling open the door and say, "Fly, be free, pretty human boy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那是赤裸裸的背叛\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That... That would be a direct betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来坐下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Come and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你一个人活不过一天\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Also, you'd survive less than a day on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你说得很对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, OK, that's completely true
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能马上就死掉了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I would die almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在整个谈判中 你只有一个优势\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You only have one advantage in this whole negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道这是不是优势\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not sure it's an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我以为你要说的话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That wasn't what I was expecting to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你以为你的优势是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, what did you think your advantage was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我用魔法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You want me to do my human magic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给卡米拉建造一支怪物大军\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to give Carmilla an army of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天我偷听了莫拉娜和斯崔格的对话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was eavesdropping on Morana and Striga during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们可以收买雇佣军来充实军队\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They can buy mercenaries to fill out the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 卡米拉放弃了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't understand. Carmilla's given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她分神了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She gets distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她称之为"天才的负担"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She calls it the burden of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们今早遗弃她 她也会好几天都发现不了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We could run out on her this morning and she wouldn't notice for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忠于我的姐妹们...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm loyal to my sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的做法并不对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but what we're doing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以离开 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We could just leave, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想跟我在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If you want to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该怎么打开无限回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}how does someone open the Infinite Corridor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一种令人震惊的意志行为\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's an appalling act of will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既要古老的知识 又要牺牲你灵魂的一部分\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A combination of ancient knowledge and sacrificing something of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 也没办法精确控制\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And it's still impossible to control with any accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你能做到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次开门 我花了一年时间才恢复\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It took me a year to recover from the last time I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能确定修道士们真的不知道回廊的入口在下面吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we're sure the monks don't know an entrance to the Corridor is down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不知道 人眼看不见\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Absolutely. It's invisible to the human eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我需要宝石\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's why I need the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们犯了一个严重的错误\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think we've made a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉院长\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Prior Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你只是一个单纯的修道士的时候\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}When you were a simple man of the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我容忍了你对我的人民的控制\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I tolerated your hold on my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你成了躲避人民的疯狂隐士时 我依然容忍了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}When you became a mad hermit who shunned my people, I tolerated you still.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须让出修道院 出来的时候扔掉武器\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You will vacate the priory. Throw your weapons out as you exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉 我知道你已经亵渎了修道院\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sala! I know you have deconsecrated the priory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝已经不在里面了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God is no longer in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有谁保护你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You enjoy no protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来 全部出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Out! All of you! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我们就进去了 萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or we come for you, Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时辰已到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is time.
